{"word":"G2218 - ζυγός - zygós - dzoo-gos' - Pair of balances","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ζυγός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>zygós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>dzoo-gos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Pair of balances"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நுகம், தராசு, நுகத்தடி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a yoke"},{"paragraph":"2. a balance, pair of scales"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the root of <b>&#x03B6;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03BD;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>zeugnumi</b> (to <i>join</i>, especially by a &ldquo;yoke&rdquo;); a <i>coupling</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>servitude</i> (a <i>law</i> or <i>obligation</i>); also (literally) the <i>beam</i> of the balance (as <i>connecting</i> the scales): - pair of balances, yoke."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2086 - ἑτεροζυγέω - heterozygéō - het-er-od-zoog-eh'-o/2086\">G2086</a>, <a href=\"#/G2218 - ζυγός - zygós - dzoo-gos'/2218\">G2218</a>"}]}